menuconfig EXAMPLES_UART_RX
	bool "uart_rx"
	default n
	---help---
		Enable the ESP32 UART receiver and esp32_uart_frame uORB publisher.

		The module defaults to /dev/ttyS4 at 115200 baud, which is TELEM2
		on the PX4 FMUv6X board. It accepts only complete frames in the format
		AA 55 payload[3] 0D 0A and publishes the raw 7-byte frame on uORB.
